      "description": "Experimental validation of CFD hemolysis predictions against in-vitro measurements for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump. Flow rates 2.0–6.0 L/min, rotational speeds 2 000–3 600 RPM. RH index agreement within 12% across all five operating points. Dataset collected and analysis completed in Q3 2019, prior to any paediatric use expansion.",
      "validationDate": "2019-09-15",
