      "rationale": "Blood analogue viscosity and density sourced from ASTM F1841 standard. Pump geometry dimensions taken from FDA benchmark model specification. Inlet flow rates and rotational speeds specified per IEC 60601-2-16 test protocol. All inputs documented in simulation input deck SI-2019-CBP-01."
